<paragraph id="88D949EF3DBCCE1BE3A029C7C2F75676" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">
<taxonomicName id="9FF6C905FC660473B12A632F5A376149" authority="(L.) Willd." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Xeranthemum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="405" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="inapertum">
Xeranthemum 
<normalizedToken id="289915331476E51A92E7D9954F500AF0" originalValue="inapértum" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">inapertum</normalizedToken>
(
<authorityName id="131D53E55763CFAF8A3023AAE6BA3763" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">L.</authorityName>
) Willd.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="A76D3FC7C8C468E477885C43F4706CF0" pageId="null" pageNumber="405" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="B0483820E3BDB08744A26D8C39C2A289" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Geschlossene Strohblume</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="AC87A660A7C176561B1AF80B09769930" pageId="null" pageNumber="405" type="description">
<paragraph id="B1A056C744DE5A509BAE1E901405C63C" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">
15-50 cm hoch. Stengel einfach oder oberhalb der Mitte verzweigt. 
<normalizedToken id="25B55B414D1AA968F900DE37DF1BFCAD" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
bis 6 cm lang und 0,7 cm breit, kurz zugespitzt. 
<normalizedToken id="1AFA11DDC58AD3D7702A801AF4A9F3BF" originalValue="Köpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Koepfe</normalizedToken>
im 
<normalizedToken id="E13CF2804F27EE81D8AE205F472F815D" originalValue="blühenden" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">bluehenden</normalizedToken>
Zustand 
<emphasis id="55CCD9B1E49EAD10EC8F3CAFA20BDF52" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">1</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="9529A0AD578C86CA789BBA543DF29A2A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">1,5 cm im Durchmesser</emphasis>
, 30-40- 
<normalizedToken id="F518F511CCE24449DC2ADA88BAE2D936" originalValue="blütig" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">bluetig</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="99158CD5F57708851EEA21A6D2378733" originalValue="Äußere" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Aeussere</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="86460563A4EC03EA6A764C540CAC8367" originalValue="Hüllblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Huellblaetter</normalizedToken>
kurz zugespitzt, 
<normalizedToken id="D759F6F6B6726468E4C50BD5A9686B51" originalValue="weißlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">weisslich</normalizedToken>
, kahl, die innersten kaum doppelt so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="93F907A9E41EC1ACBFBC6915AC7BBD2A" originalValue="äußern" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">aeussern</normalizedToken>
, 
<emphasis id="BABE13CA52C638FDD16F5C21BC530BE1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">10</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="3FD0D36219AFA8602FD85C210F0FBD51" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">15 mm lang und 1,5</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="1D97BF02FA6FFD081A0969FF29CC53CE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">
3 mm breit, auf der Innenseite rosa, zur 
<normalizedToken id="18255850D2D15530F0375E509D3E9451" originalValue="Blütezeit" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Bluetezeit</normalizedToken>
aufrecht.
</emphasis>
Kronen rotviolett. 
<emphasis id="7F5764D90FADC9E81B0711373C2DF2E4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">
<normalizedToken id="0EB61C238CE7116C8A0B494581C08F0F" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
5
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="059CC414DC21CF0CE05E3C9FFE9CB263" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">
6 mm lang. 
<taxonomicName id="B545B90CE0C951D47DB3D5DFAD403377" class="Insecta" family="Miridae" genus="Pappus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="405" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Pappus</taxonomicName>
etwa 5 mm lang
</emphasis>
, aus 5 Schuppen bestehend. - 
<normalizedToken id="0DA369660D83B7595167DC7FFF3057D8" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="25345E2B542AE46DCC5196CA4DC9CFD8" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">
<emphasis id="533C052E06E589A4556E79931AE22F37" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="370892E77E0275D75C9B003B3684D604" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">
<emphasis id="F22CFCA85396CD2885FFD5BC705C9543" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan. Trockene, steinige 
<normalizedToken id="EEE7BE2B6B1B57236FDD0DCCF4C97B30" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. Lichte 
<normalizedToken id="C706D774C88AFB0143E14B47D68E1B29" originalValue="Föhrenwälder" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Foehrenwaelder</normalizedToken>
, Felsensteppen, 
<normalizedToken id="430D32876FA4AD329C3057778F8D559A" originalValue="Äcker" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Aecker</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F4736A88216585A943C5DBE474261C71" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">
<emphasis id="A12EC02BD2E4729700E3A6C22E12F0F7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Verbreitung. Mediterrane Pflanze:</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="91F4E18B260DFF83E7AB203854CFE022" originalValue="Südeuropa" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Suedeuropa</normalizedToken>
(
<normalizedToken id="D7D10DD901FAF4FEAA185CFF22FF929F" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Mittelfrankreich, Wallis, 
<normalizedToken id="C9140783A5DB2959F9F9891C194E9E3D" originalValue="Alpensüdfuß" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Alpensuedfuss</normalizedToken>
, Dalmatien, Mazedonien); Kleinasien, Syrien; Nordafrika. - Im Gebiet: 
<normalizedToken id="489D39A636B2B713589C3BBE18BFA67F" originalValue="Dép" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Dep</normalizedToken>
. Ain (
<normalizedToken id="E6126FFED555F1F09F4DA3771F6E0267" originalValue="Méximieux" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Meximieux</normalizedToken>
), Savoyen (Maurienne, Tarentaise), Wallis (Vernayaz bis 
<normalizedToken id="889882B0BF70DFF022E5605A5C368DD1" originalValue="Mörel" pageId="null" pageNumber="405">Moerel</normalizedToken>
), Aostatal (St-Denis bis St-Nicolas), Gegend von Como.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
